-abandona |publisher=futbol.univision.com |accessdate=2015-07-23 |language=es |date=2015-07-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723184457/http://futbol.univision.com/article/2403018/2015-07-16/copa-oro/cuba/ariel-martinez-tambien-abandona |archivedate=2015-07-23 }}</ref>

*古巴隊的總教練{{le|勞爾·岡薩雷斯·特里亞納|Raúl González Triana}}與{{le|阿德里安·迪茲|Adrián Diz}}、{{le|艾驰尔·赫尔南德斯|Arichel Hernández}}、{{le|丹尼爾·路易斯|Daniel Luís}}、{{le|安迪·巴克羅|Andy Vaquero}}、{{le|米高·利耶斯|Maikel Reyes}}、{{le|桑迪·桑切斯|Sandy Sánchez}}6名主力隊員，在第一場小組賽對墨西哥前，因[[美簽|美簽]]問題被拒於海關之外。這些人員都曾參加先前於安地卡及巴布達舉辦的{{le|2015年中北美洲及加勒比海區奧運資格錦標賽|2015 CONCACAF Men's Olympic Qualifying Championship qualification}}，當時已經發生過類似問題。因總教練與6名主力隊員被拒於海關之外，再加上前鋒加西亞的投誠，導致古巴隊在第一場小組賽對墨西哥時只有16名球員在場。<ref>{{cite web|title=Keilen García desertó de la selección de Cuba|trans_title=Keilen García deserts the Cuban national team|url=http://futbol.univision.com/article/2394482/2015-07-08/copa-oro/cuba/keilen-garcia-deserto-de-la|publisher=futbol.univision.com|accessdate=2015-07-09|language=es|date=2015-07-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150710083943/http://futbol.univision.com/article/2394482/2015-07-08/copa-oro/cuba/keilen-garcia-deserto-de-la|archivedate=2015-07-10}}</ref>古巴中場{{le|艾驰尔·赫尔南德斯|Arichel Hernández}}最後因[[美簽|美簽]]問題無法解決，因而無法在本屆賽事出場。<ref>{{cite web |title=Deserta segundo jugador de Cuba en la Copa de Oro |url=http://feeds.univision.com/feeds/article/2015-07-12/deserta-segundo-jugador-de-cuba?refPath=/futbol |publisher=Univision.com |accessdate=2015-07-23 |language=es |date=2015-07-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723184647/http://feeds.univision.com/feeds/article/2015-07-12/deserta-segundo-jugador-de-cuba?refPath=%2Ffutbol |archivedate=2015-07-23 }}</ref>

*哥斯大黎加隊在半準決賽對墨西哥時，瓜地馬拉籍主審裁判{{link-en|沃爾特·洛佩茲|Walter López Castellanos}}依照助理裁判埃里克·鮑里斯（Eric Boria）的判決，認為在第124分鐘加時賽補時時，哥斯大黎加後衛{{le|羅伊·米勒|Roy Miller (footballer)}}在禁區衝撞墨西哥前鋒[[奧里比·佩拉爾塔|奧里比·佩拉爾塔]]犯規，讓墨西哥獲得[[十二碼|十二碼]]罰球機會，墨西哥靠著隊長[[安德雷斯·瓜爾達多|安德雷斯·瓜爾達多]]罰進一球，以1-0擊敗哥斯大黎加。<ref>{{cite web |title=Así fue el escandaloso penalti que clasificó a México |url=http://www.marca.com/2015/07/20/futbol/copa-oro/1437373066.html |publisher=MARCA.com |accessdate=2015-07-23 |language=es |date=2015-07-15 |archive-date=2015-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722234621/http://www.marca.com/2015/07/20/futbol/copa-oro/1437373066.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>哥斯大黎加當地報紙{{link-en|La Nación|La Nación (San José)}}刊登此判決根本是小偷行徑，哥斯大黎加隊總教練為此緩頰，認為主審裁判對該判決有他的道理在。<ref>{{cite web |title=Costa Rica manager Paulo Wanchope reacts to last-minute loss vs. Mexico in Gold Cup quarters |url=http://prosoccertalk.nbcsports.com/2015/07/20/costa-rica-manager-paulo-wanchope-reacts-to-last-minute-loss-vs-mexico-in-gold-cup-quarters/ |publisher=NBC Sports |accessdate=2015-07-23 |language= |date=2015-07-20 |archive-date=2015-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722205225/http://prosoccertalk.nbcsports.com/2015/07/20/costa-rica-manager-paulo-wanchope-reacts-to-last-minute-loss-vs-mexico-in-gold-cup-quarters/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>米勒則認為該判決太誇張，宣稱他與佩拉爾塔只有輕微的接觸。<ref>{{cite web |title=VIDEO: Roy Miller sobre el penal: "Se tira, exagera Oribe Peralta" |url=http://www.diez.hn/internacionales/860807-99/roy-miller-sobre-el-penal-se-tira-exagera-oribe-peralta |publisher=diez.hn |accessdate=2015-07-23 |language=es |date=2015-07-20 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723215748/http://www.diez.hn/internacionales/860807-99/roy-miller-sobre-el-penal-se-tira-exagera-oribe-peralta |dead-url=no }}</ref>洛佩茲在7月23日接受當地報紙{{link-en|Prensa Libre|Prensa Libre}}訪問後坦承，該判罰是他誤判，稱當時他所在的位置無法看到真實情況，只能靠助理裁判協助。<ref>{{cite web |title=López: No era penal |url=http://www.prensalibre.com/PrensaLibreTV/DetalleTV/431991 |publisher=Prensa Libre |accessdate=2015-07-24 |language=es |date=2015-07-23 |archive-date=2015-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724115006/http://www.prensalibre.com/PrensaLibreTV/DetalleTV/431991 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Walter López lo admite, no era penal para México |url=http://www.foxdeportes.com/copa-oro/story/walter-lopez-lo-admite-no-era-penal-para-mexico/ |publisher=ESPN.com.mx |accessdate=2015-07-24 |language=es |date=2015-07-23 |archive-date=2015-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150803185503/http://www.foxdeportes.com/copa-oro/story/walter-lopez-lo-admite-no-era-penal-para-mexico/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

*巴拿馬隊在準決賽對墨西哥時，因美國籍主審裁判[[馬克·基格|馬克·基格]]在第24分鐘時，認為巴拿馬前鋒{{le|路爾斯·特哈達|Luis Tejada}}與墨西哥球員有肢體衝突嫌疑，做出爭議性紅牌判罰，導致巴拿馬後來只有10人在場上。<ref name="Nytimes">{{cite web |title=Messy Mexico-Panama Semifinal Leaves a Stain on Concacaf |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/24/sports/soccer/messy-mexico-panama-semifinal-worthy-of-concacaf.html?_r=0 |publisher=nytimes.com |accessdate= |language= |date=2015-07-23 |archive-date=2015-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727114829/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/24/sports/soccer/messy-mexico-panama-semifinal-worthy-of-concacaf.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MP">{{cite web |title=中北美洲金盃》2個12碼罰球 墨西哥逆轉晉決賽 |url=http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1388525 |publisher=自由電子報 |accessdate= |language= |date=2015-07-23 |archive-date=2015-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801051642/http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1388525 |dead-url=no }}</ref>後來在第88分鐘時，因巴拿馬後衛{{le|羅曼·托雷斯|Román Torres}}在禁區內與墨西哥中場{{le|卡洛斯·埃斯基韋爾|Carlos Esquivel}}爭球中因重心不穩而向後跌倒碰到球<ref>{{cite web |title=Panama got screwed by a bogus 89th-minute penalty against Mexico and then went ballistic |url=http://www.businessinsider.com.au/gold-cup-panama-mexico-penalty-2015-7 |publisher=businessinsider.com |accessdate= |language= |date=2015-07-23 |archive-date=2015-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150809062628/http://www.businessinsider.com.au/gold-cup-panama-mexico-penalty-2015-7 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MP"/>，主審裁判馬克·基格認為此舉有手球嫌疑，依照FIFA規則<ref>{{cite web |title=Laws of the Game |url=http://www.fifa.com/development/education-and-technical/referees/laws-of-the-game.html |publisher=FIFA |accessdate=2015-07-23 |language= |date=2015-02-28 |archive-date=2015-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150810011223/http://www.fifa.com/development/education-and-technical/referees/laws-of-the-game.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>判給墨西哥一個[[十二碼|十二碼]]罰球機會<ref name="Nytimes"/><ref>{{cite web |title=Watch: Penalty call sets up Mexico go-ahead goal in win vs. Panama |url=http://www.si.com/planet-futbol/2015/07/23/gold-cup-mexico-panama-video-andres-guardado-penalty-goal |publisher=SI |accessdate=2015-07-23 |language= |date=2015-07-23 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723231423/http://www.si.com/planet-futbol/2015/07/23/gold-cup-mexico-panama-video-andres-guardado-penalty-goal |dead-url=no }}</ref>，此判罰讓巴拿馬球員不滿而與墨西哥隊員及大會人員發生衝突，巴拿馬球員甚至宣稱要罷賽，場外球迷也投擲紙杯或其他物品到場內表示不滿，場上一度呈失控狀態而暫停比賽一段時間，巴拿馬球員則在衝突10分鐘後返回球場繼續比賽。<ref name="Record">{{cite web |title=Jugadores de Panamá mostraron sentirse robados |url=http://www.record.com.mx/articulo/noticias/4254614/copa-oro+mexico/jugadores-de-panama-abandonan-el-campo-tras-polemico-penalti |publisher=Récord |accessdate=2015-07-23 |language=es |date=2015-07-22 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723150502/http://www.record.com.mx/articulo/noticias/4254614/copa-oro+mexico/jugadores-de-panama-abandonan-el-campo-tras-polemico-penalti |dead-url=no }}</ref>此判罰因墨西哥隊長[[安德雷斯·瓜爾達多|安德雷斯·瓜爾達多]]罰進一球，導致墨西哥以1-1追平巴拿馬，讓該場比賽必須進入延長賽，墨西哥隨後再第105分中靠著第二個[[十二碼|十二碼]]罰球，以2-1擊敗巴拿馬。<ref name="MP"/><ref>{{cite web |title=Con polémica: México venció a Panamá y jugará final de Copa Oro |url=http://elcomercio.pe/deporte-total/futbol-mundial/mexico-vs-panama-juegan-semifinal-copa-oro-2015-noticia-1827553 |publisher=El Comercio |accessdate=2015-07-23 |language=es |date=2015-07-22 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723124357/http://elcomercio.pe/deporte-total/futbol-mundial/mexico-vs-panama-juegan-semifinal-copa-oro-2015-noticia-1827553 |dead-url=no }}</ref>巴拿馬球員在比賽結束後，因不滿裁判該場的判決，衝向裁判群追打裁判，該場裁判群最後靠著大會人員的護送才得以離場。<ref name="MP2">{{cite web |title=中北美洲金盃》爭議判決下吞敗 巴拿馬場上直接踢裁判 |url=http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1389529 |publisher=自由電子報 |accessdate= |language= |date=2015-07-24 |archive-date=2015-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150802154254/http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1389529 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Panama players storm after referee following controversial Gold Cup loss |url=http://www.sbnation.com/lookit/2015/7/23/9019683/panama-players-storm-after-referee-following-controversial-gold-cup |publisher=sbnation.com |accessdate= |language= |date=2015-07-23 |archive-date=2015-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725230917/http://www.sbnation.com/lookit/2015/7/23/9019683/panama-players-storm-after-referee-following-controversial-gold-cup |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Gold Cup semifinal at Dome turns chaotic |url=http://www.ajc.com/news/sports/pro-sports/gold-cup-semifinal-at-dome-turns-chaotic/nm5Y5/ |publisher=ajc.com |accessdate= |language= |date=2015-07-23 |archive-date=2015-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727075454/http://www.ajc.com/news/sports/pro-sports/gold-cup-semifinal-at-dome-turns-chaotic/nm5Y5/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>瓜爾達多賽後採訪中表示，第88分鐘對巴拿馬的判決是重傷害，他也曾考慮過是否該放水踢不進罰球。<ref>{{cite web |title=Mexico's Guardado thought about missing penalty kick on purpose |url=http://www.cbssports.com/general/eye-on-sports/25248026/panama-almost-walks-off-field-after-questionable-pk-given-to-mexico |publisher=CBS Sports |accessdate= |language= |date=2015-07-22 |archive-date=2015-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725015920/http://www.cbssports.com/general/eye-on-sports/25248026/panama-almost-walks-off-field-after-questionable-pk-given-to-mexico |dead-url=no }}</ref>墨西哥總教練{{le|米格爾·艾雷拉|Miguel Herrera}}雖在賽後採訪中表示，第88分鐘對巴拿馬的判決有問題<ref name="MP2"/>，但認為瓜爾達多不需要也沒必要放水踢不進罰球，艾雷拉引用2014年世界盃足球賽十六強賽[[2014年世界盃足球賽相關問題#荷蘭_v._墨西哥|墨西哥對荷蘭爭議]]，認為當時爭議判決主審裁判照樣給荷蘭罰球機會，讓墨西哥在比賽中被擊敗。<ref>{{cite web |title=Mexico reach Gold Cup final but Panama furious after penalty call |url=http://www.espnfc.us/concacaf-gold-cup/59/blog/post/2532801/mexico-panama-gold-cup-penalty-controversy |publisher=ESPNFC.us |accessdate= |language= |date=2015-07-23 |archive-date=2015-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150806031819/http://www.espnfc.us/concacaf-gold-cup/59/blog/post/2532801/mexico-panama-gold-cup-penalty-controversy |dead-url=no }}</ref>7月24日，中北美洲及加勒比海足球協會紀律委員會針對巴拿馬守門員{{le|海梅·裴尼多|Jaime Penedo}}在場上污辱裁判一事，作出禁賽兩場處分，裴尼多最後無法在本屆季軍賽，以及11月的[[2018年世界盃外圍賽_(中北美洲及加勒比海區)|世界盃資格賽]]上場。因紅牌下場的前鋒特哈達，也因污辱裁判，再加罰禁賽一場。<ref>{{cite web |title=Jaime Penedo suspendido dos partidos y 15 mil dólares de multa a Panamá |url=http://www.rpctv.com/copaoro/noticias/Penedo-suspendido-partidos-dolares-multa_0_828217897.html |publisher=rpctv.com |accessdate= |language= |date=2015-07-24 |archive-date=2015-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150726223510/http://www.rpctv.com/copaoro/noticias/Penedo-suspendido-partidos-dolares-multa_0_828217897.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*巴拿馬隊在準決賽對墨西哥結束後，因不滿裁判判決，在更衣室揮舞著''CONCACAF是小偷''（CONCACAF Ladrones）的旗幟，旗幟下方並寫著三個''腐敗''，所有球員們都以大拇指向下的手勢對[[中北美洲及加勒比海足球協會|中北美洲及加勒比海足球協會]]表達不滿，該照片隨後在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上流傳。<ref>{{cite web |title=Tras polémica con Tri, Panamá llama 'ladrones corruptos' a CONCACAF |url=http://espndeportes.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/2428897/tras-polemica-con-tri-panama-llama-ladrones-corruptos-a-concacaf |publisher=ESPN.com.mx |accessdate=2015-07-23 |language=es |date=2015-07-22 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723135125/http://espndeportes.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/2428897/tras-polemica-con-tri-panama-llama-ladrones-corruptos-a-concacaf |dead-url=no }}</ref>中北美洲及加勒比海足球協會紀律委員會隨後對此行為，向[[巴拿馬足球協會|巴拿馬足球協會]]開出15,000美元罰款。<ref>{{cite web |title=Jaime Penedo suspendido dos partidos y 15 mil dólares de multa a Panamá |url=http://www.rpctv.com/copaoro/noticias/Penedo-suspendido-partidos-dolares-multa_0_828217897.html |publisher=rpctv.com |accessdate= |language=es |date=2015-07-24 |archive-date=2015-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150726223510/http://www.rpctv.com/copaoro/noticias/Penedo-suspendido-partidos-dolares-multa_0_828217897.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*[[哥斯大黎加足球協會|哥斯大黎加足球協會]]與[[巴拿馬足球協會|巴拿馬足球協會]]因對本屆賽事判罰不滿，於7月23日爭對爭議判罰，要求[[中北美洲及加勒比海足球協會|中北美洲及加勒比海足球協會]]裁判委員會開除有爭議性判罰的裁判，並公開呼籲中北美洲及加勒比海足球協會裁判委員會必須放棄個人的立場，站在公正角度做出決定。<ref>{{cite web |title=FEDEFUTBOL exige cambios en CONCACAF |url=http://fedefutbolcr.com/fedefutbol-exige-cambios-en-concacaf/ |publisher=FEDEFUTBOLCR.com |accessdate= |language=es |date=2015-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724112133/http://fedefutbolcr.com/fedefutbol-exige-cambios-en-concacaf/ |archive-date=2015-07-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>中北美洲及加勒比海足球協會則回應將會開執行委員會會議討論此事。<ref>{{cite web |title=CONCACAF Statement regarding official requests from Costa Rica Football Federation and Panama Football Federation |url=http://www.concacaf.com/article/concacaf-statement-regarding-official-requests-from-costa-rica-football-federation-and-panama-football-federation |publisher=concacaf.com |accessdate= |language= |date=2015-07-24 |archive-date=2015-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150728030840/http://www.concacaf.com/article/concacaf-statement-regarding-official-requests-from-costa-rica-football-federation-and-panama-football-federation |dead-url=no }}</ref>

